import styles from './wishList.module.scss' import TopNavBar from 'components/TopNavBar' import { HeartIcon } from 'assets/svgs' import { MouseEvent } from 'react' import store from 'store' interface SearchStructure { authors: string[] contents: string datetime: string isbn: string price: number publisher: string sale_price: number status: string thumbnail: string title: string translators: any[] url: string } const WishList = () => { const storeData = store.get('likeStore') return (
{storeData.length > 0 ? (
    {storeData.map((item: SearchStructure) => (
  • {item.title}
    {item.authors}
    {item.price}원
    • ))}
) : (
좋아요를 누른 항목이 없습니다.
)}
) } export default WishList
